<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich Nothafft zu Wernberg, Viztum in Niederbayern</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt die wegen der Forderung Herzog Ludwigs VII. von Bayern-Ingolstadt notwendige Verschiebung des Gerichtstags zu Straubing mit Friedrich von Egloffstein und Georg Truchseß von Holnstein auf Dienstag nach Oculi.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_267" id="133v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_267_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft ʒu <expan>vvermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l2">vıcʒtum Jn nider payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_267_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe Der <expan>hochgeb<ex>orn</ex></expan> fürſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l4">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> von payern eẅch vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex>ſchaft</expan> gen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l5">Jngolſtat <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hab auf den ſunntag <expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l6">Jr bey dem tag den Jr vns gen <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein vnd ~ dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l7"><expan>Truchſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . auf den Ertag nach <expan>Remi<ex>ni</ex>ſce<ex>re</ex></expan> <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> hett niht geſeın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l8">mugt . vnd begert daʒ wır <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag acht tag <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lengen</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l9">auf den Ertag nach dem ſunntag Oculȷ ſuchen <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l10">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l11"><expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . auf den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Ertag nach dem ſunntag Oculȷ . für eẅch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l12">gen Strawbıng <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . in <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> maſſ als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l13">nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_267_r1l14">lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> künigundıs </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_267" id="133v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Nothaft zu
                        <expan>Wermb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, vicztum in Nider Payern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vicztum, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie der
                                <expan>hochgeb<ex>orn</ex></expan> fürst und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> von Payern ewch und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ritt<ex>er</ex>schaft</expan> gen Ingolstat
                            <expan>geford<ex>er</ex>t</expan> hab auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">sunntag
                                        <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan>
                                schierist</q>15.03.1416</note>
</app>, daz ir bey dem tag, den ir uns gen <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        vom Eglofstein und dem <expan>Truchsess<ex>en</ex></expan> auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">ertag nach
                                        <expan>remi<ex>ni</ex>sce<ex>re</ex></expan></q>17.03.1416</note>
</app>
<expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan> hett niht gesein mugt, und begert, daz
                        wir <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag acht tag
                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lengen</expan> und auf den <app><note><q type="date">ertag nach dem sunntag
                            oculi</q>24.03.1416</note></app> suchen <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Und tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                        unser <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auf den
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> ertag nach dem sunntag oculi für
                        ewch gen Strawbing <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> in <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> mass, als
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Künigundis. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
